{"id": "1255540440254648361", "channel_id": "1255540440254648361", "type": 0, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "把更新后的故事RE了一下，发现两边没有修改到的小虫。\n\nP1：“主祭眼神里不再有锐利和威严”\n新剧情里此时老主祭已经退位，应改为“老主祭”。\n\nP2：“侍卫们并不知道这位新任主祭的想要做什么”两处错误。\n1. 新故事里弥利亚姆已成为主祭多年，不应当是“新任主祭”。 \n2. “新任主祭的想要做什么”，这个“的”大概是文案手误。", "timestamp": "2024-06-26T15:09:27.770000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-26T15:10:44.717000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1255540440632131654", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-26-21-42-45-261_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 104207, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255540440254648361/1255540440632131654/Screenshot_2024-06-26-21-42-45-261_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cc8c67&is=69cb3ae7&hm=c117a3b9ba5401fecc6a0d373fcfc1b38159e41d65ad2177d87fa8d419e91e94&"}, {"id": "1255540440963223585", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-26-21-52-08-638_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 77805, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255540440254648361/1255540440963223585/Screenshot_2024-06-26-21-52-08-638_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cc8c67&is=69cb3ae7&hm=b2a2d785b1c71ec4011b7ea7487539456bea7760bf6ff369f68c822e957f9a04&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255540440254648361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」抓一点改版后米粒支线的文本错误", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
